{"lemma":"صِلاتُ","slug":"صِلاتُ","root":"#.ص.ل","root_slug":"_-ص-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ص-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24653","n24654","n24655"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%90%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of وَصَلَ (waṣala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"link, connection"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of وَصَلَ (waṣala, “to connect”), from the root و ص ل (w ṣ l)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24653","headword_ar":"صَلَّةٌ","root":"Sl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[as an inf. n. of un.] The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound of a nail"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, when it is struck with force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sil~apN","text_ar":"صِلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lijaAm","text_ar":"لِجَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bit"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dry ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land, not rained upon, between two tracts of ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land, that are rained upon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) because, being dry, it makes a sound [when trodden upon]: (M:) or accord. to IDrd,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land, rained upon, between two tracts not rained upon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) or simply"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whatever it be;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAhirapN","text_ar":"سَاهِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SilaAlN","text_ar":"صِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sole:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [ISd says,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuf~N jay~idu AlS~al~api","text_ar":"خُفٌّ جَيِّدُ الصَّلَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A boot good"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of the sole;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is thus called by the name of the ground, not otherwise; in my opinion because of its dryness, and its making a sound on the occasion of treading. (M. [See also another explanation of this phrase in what follows.]) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Skin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuf~N jay~idu AlS~al~api","text_ar":"خُفٌّ جَيِّدُ الصَّلَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A boot good in respect of the skin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"somewhat differently expl. above]: (S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dry skin, before the tanning."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stinking skin in the tan."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An extensive rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a scattered, scanty rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sal~N","text_ar":"صَلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sil~N","text_ar":"صِلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": thus having two contr. meanings: (K:) pl. as above: (M:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SilaAlN","text_ar":"صِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", its pl., signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portions of scattered rains, falling by little and little."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) ―         -b5-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a scattered portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of herbage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) pl. as above: (M:) or [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SilaAlN","text_ar":"صِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is thus called by the name of the rain. (S, O.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Moist earth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b7-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sul~apN","text_ar":"صُلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-  Also The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisot","text_ar":"اِسْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"podex,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anus"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n24654","headword_ar":"صُلَّةٌ","root":"Sl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sal~apN","text_ar":"صَلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in the O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Remains of water"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a watering-trough;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus expl. by Fr; (O;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of other things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the oils called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duhon","text_ar":"دُهْن"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zayot","text_ar":"زَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuloSulapN","text_ar":"صُلْصُلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A fetid odour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flabbiness of moist flesh-meat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","O"]},{"entry_id":"n24655","headword_ar":"صِلَّةٌ","root":"Sl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sal~apN","text_ar":"صَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa tiboEu Sil~apK","text_ar":"هُوَ تِبْعُ صِلَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"D","text_ar":"ض"},{"kind":"text","text":", [i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dil~apK","text_ar":"ضِلَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] accord. to different relaters, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is a very cunning man"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAhiyapN","text_ar":"دَاهِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one in whom is no good."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}